import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form'

const ViaCep = () =>{
    const {register, handleSubmit} = useForm()

    const onSubmit = (e) =>{
        console.log(e)
    }
    return(
        <form onSubmit={handleSubmit(onSubmit)} style={{ color:'#ffffff', flexDirection: 'column' }} >
            <label >
                CEP:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
            <label >
                Logradouro:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
            <label >
                Complemento:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
            <label >
                Bairro:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
            <label >
                Cidade:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
            <label >
                Estado:
                <input type='text' {...register('cep')} />
            </label>
        </form>
    )
}

export default ViaCep
